message: "If you use this registry or methodology, please cite as below."
title: "Tai Po Wang Fuk Court Citizen Archive: Registry and Preservation Risk Assessment"
abstract: >
  Structured registry and preservation risk assessment of 21 citizen-led
  digital archives documenting the 2025 Wang Fuk Court fire (Tai Po, Hong
  Kong). Developed within a post-custodial archival framework, with Dublin
  Core metadata, EDTF date encoding, and a six-dimension risk assessment
  that integrates ethical review as a first-class preservation dimension.
  Project developed with AI-assisted technical execution (Anthropic Claude)
  under author's intellectual direction, theoretical framing, and validation.
type: dataset
version: "1.1.0"
date-released: "2026-04-16"
license: CC-BY-4.0
keywords:
  - citizen archives
  - digital preservation
  - crisis informatics
  - Hong Kong
  - Wang Fuk Court
  - Tai Po fire
  - Dublin Core
  - EDTF
